narratives.question_text: Use the space below to comment on questions 1-10, if you wish
comments: I learned I have so much to learn from my peers, it has not always been so obvious to me, I am pretty much concentrated on my own work.
Discussion on other matters, publications, ethical concerns.. exchange of experiences between students. Some students are willing to share more than others, as obvious.

narratives.question_text: The things about this course most in need of improvement are:
comments: Less need to show off would be great! it is a contagious trap.

narratives.question_text: What was the availability and quality of help you received of the instructor and TA?
Discuss if you wish how this course fits into your overall program.
comments: it is one of the few occasions I can think about my work.

narratives.question_text: Why did you take this course?
comments: it is an honor to take it. I look forward to it more and more.

narratives.question_text: Did it live up to your expectations?
comments: Last year, at first, I did not understand what it was for, so my expectations lowered down. It made up for it later.

narratives.question_text: Did you get out of it what you expected?
comments: Yes, but I look forward to the next course!
